android.car.telemetry

接口 CarTelemetryManager.MetricsReportCallback

  • 封闭类:
    CarTelemetryManager

    public static interface CarTelemetryManager.MetricsReportCallback
    Application must pass a CarTelemetryManager.MetricsReportCallback object to receive finished reports from CarTelemetryManager.getFinishedReport(String, Executor, MetricsReportCallback) and CarTelemetryManager.getAllFinishedReports(Executor, MetricsReportCallback).

    • 方法概要

      Provides the metrics report associated with metricsConfigName.

    • 方法详细资料

      • onResult

        void onResult(java.lang.String metricsConfigName,
              PersistableBundle report,
              byte[] telemetryError,
              int status)
        Provides the metrics report associated with metricsConfigName. If there is a metrics report, it provides the metrics report. If the metrics report calculation failed due to a runtime error during the execution of reporting script, it provides the runtime error in the error parameter. The status parameter provides more information on the state of the metrics report. TODO(b/184964661): Publish the documentation for the format of the finished reports.
        参数:
        metricsConfigName - name of the MetricsConfig that the report is associated with.
        report - the car telemetry report. Null if there is no report.
        telemetryError - the serialized telemetry metrics configuration runtime execution error.
        status - of the metrics report. See CarTelemetryManager.MetricsReportStatus.
